<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>startHub</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html" charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            border-top-left-radius: 5px;
            border-top-right-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            color: #888888;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome to startHub </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= currUser.name %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with Koko. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>
            <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
            <p>Please enter this code on the activation code within the next few hours.</p>
            <p>If you did not register for startHub, ignore this email</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:mustafatahir@gmail.com">contact us</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
